Zookeeper to manage Kafka cluster:
								./zookeeper-server-start.sh ../config/zookeeper.properties

Run Kafka Broker:
								./kafka-server-start.sh ../config/server.properties

Creating Kafka topic:
					 			./kafka-topics.sh --create --topic myTopic -zookeeper localhost:2181 --replication-factor 1 --partitions 1

LINK: 
								http://localhost:8080/kafka/produce?message=This is my message

Creating Consumer: 
								./kafka-console-consumer.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic myTopic

Check msgs: 
								http://localhost:8080/kafka/messages

Send msg :
								http://localhost:8080/kafka/produce?message=Message sent by my App!

